    "en": {
      "title": "The oil refinery will resume work from next week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sapugaskanda Refinery, which has been closed for several weeks due to the lack of crude oil, is scheduled to start again from next week. Along with Sri Lanka getting crude oil again.",
        "A ship carrying 100,000 metric tons of crude oil reached the island yesterday and the sample testing will be done today.",
        "After that, unloading operations will be started. The work of the oil refinery is scheduled to resume after unloading the crude oil.",
        "Also, another ship carrying 120000 metric tons of crude oil is scheduled to reach Sri Lanka on 23-29."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "next week",
          "label": "DATE"
        }
      ],
